Class TreeWalker

java.lang.Object
koopa.core.trees.TreeWalker
public class TreeWalker extends Object
Utility class for walking a Tree depth-first.

      Makes it so that nothing else in the given tree will be seen.

      Note. This assumes that the current position is somewhere in the given subtree, but there is no explicit check that this is indeed true...
